{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 像素","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS_pixel","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 像素</strong>—在 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS\">CSS</a> 以 <code>px</code> 前輟表示—是大致對應單個點長高、肉眼也能輕易見到、否則就盡可能小的長度單位。按照定義，CSS 像素是在肉眼一臂之遙的距離下，像素密度（pixel density）為單個 96 DPI 像素的物理尺寸。</p>\n<p>這定義當然因為如「輕易見到」或「一臂之遙」之類的不精確、因人而異的用詞，而有很多解釋的空間：像是用戶坐在桌上型電腦前，用戶與那台電腦的距離，其實比手機還遠。</p>\n<p>因此，不管屏幕的實際像素密度多少，通常在談到 <code>px</code> 的時候，是為了想辦法讓 <code>96px</code> 與的長度等於 1 英寸（約 2.54 公分）。換句話說，如果某台手機的像素密度為 266 DPI，而某個元素的長度為 <code>96px</code>，該元素的實際長度為 266 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">設備像素</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-3/#absolute-lengths\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Values and Units Module, section 5.2: Absolute Lengths</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"學習它","title":"學習它","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2013/09/css-length-explained/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Length Explained</a> on the MDN Hacks Blog</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"CSS 像素—在 CSS 以 px 前輟表示—是大致對應單個點長高、肉眼也能輕易見到、否則就盡可能小的長度單位。按照定義，CSS 像素是在肉眼一臂之遙的距離下，像素密度（pixel density）為單個 96 DPI 像素的物理尺寸。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS pixel","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Pixel CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS pixel","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Pixel CSS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS 像素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/css_pixel","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/css_pixel/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS_pixel","title":"CSS 像素"}],"pageTitle":"CSS 像素 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}